{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-05204/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-05204"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:52:04"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["close-up"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["two shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A woman turns her head to listen to the man seated behind her."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05204/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-05204","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05204/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-05204"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05204/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05204/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05204/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05204/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05204/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05204/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05204/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05204/canvas/1/1996b086-5847-4d72-9bc7-45b4085aaa87","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T20:07:36.951Z","creator":"Tallulah Stallvik","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>When asked whether her wealth will become her husband’s property, Barbra responds that she doesn’t think so, but doesn’t know, at which point her husband jumps in and answers the question. She seemingly has made this decision without much thought, while her husband has considered the financial impacts, possibly even choosing to marry her for mercenary reasons.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05204/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:347.5895494830133,231.49533788773996,911.605197562777,598.6200609305761"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05204/canvas/1/c5bb97c6-f516-48f2-b29e-11dd4c99992f","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T20:08:03.017Z","creator":"Tallulah Stallvik","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>David C. Haymann’s biography of Barbara Hutton describes the real-life scene as follows: “Rubirosa interrupted to note that they were being married under Dominican law. ‘But in my country her money belongs to her and my money belongs to me. Anyway, I don’t need her money. I have enough of my own’ (Haymann, <em>Poor Little Rich Girl</em>, 295). The film opts to leave out any reference to Rubirosa’s affair with actress Zsa Zsa Gabor.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-05204/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:11.75612682557528,19.473905807205796,249.26837149187594,203.88894017725246"}}}]}]}]}